flowchart TD
    subgraph Online ["🗣️ 检索后：动态推理流程 (Online)"]
        User((用户)) --> Query[用户提问]
        Query --> Agent[LangGraph Agent]
        
        subgraph RAG_Engine ["🧩 Modular RAG 引擎"]
            Rewrite[✍️ Query Rewriter<br/>语义对齐] --> Search[Milvus ANN Search<br/>HNSW 粗排 Top-K]
            
            
            Decision{分数差距 < 阈值？}
            Decision -- 是 (难抉择) --> RerankFactory[🏭 RerankerFactory]
            RerankFactory -->|加载模型 | CrossEnc[⚖️ CrossEncoder 精排]
            Decision -- 否 (优势大) --> Skip[✅ 跳过重排]
            
            CrossEnc --> Final[最终上下文 Top-3]
            Skip --> Final
            Search --> Decision
        end
        
        subgraph Memory_System ["💾 记忆系统"]
            Redis[(Redis: 短期会话)]
            MySQL[(MySQL: 长期画像)]
            MemTools[Memory Tools]
        end
        
        Agent -- 调用 --> RAG_Engine
        Agent -- 调用 --> Memory_System
        
        Final --> LLM[LLM 生成答案]
        MemTools --> LLM
        Redis -.-> Agent
        MySQL -.-> MemTools
    end

    LLM --> Response[最终回复<br/>带引用来源]
    Response --> User
    
    style Online fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#e65100
    style RAG_Engine fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#4a148c
    style Factory fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#fbc02d,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style RerankFactory fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#fbc02d,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Memory_System fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#1b5e20